		{"id":"d0eef5c658b3a60e","type":"text","text":"**Notes**\n- structs are stored inline, this restricts the types that can be represented\n- Godot doesn't have a concept of structs, but some variant types are under the hood and can be used as such","x":2720,"y":1760,"width":580,"height":180},
		{"id":"ae1e26cb0c54830f","type":"text","text":"**Notes**\n- ","x":2060,"y":1760,"width":580,"height":80},
