		{"id":"629c918a2125ea6d","type":"text","text":"**Notes**\n- ","x":1380,"y":1760,"width":580,"height":100},
		{"id":"461a13d5e9ddac0b","type":"text","text":"- [ ] object-api with metadata: `(native:ident)`\n- [ ] empty table\n- [ ] inline field types\n    - [ ] scalar values\n    - [ ] struct\n    - [ ] array\n- [ ] offset field types\n    - [ ] table\n    - [ ] union\n    - [ ] vector","x":2060,"y":1860,"width":580,"height":360},
		{"id":"57eec75def1119ca","type":"text","text":"- [ ] empty struct\n- [ ] inline types\n    - [ ] struct\n    - [ ] scalars / enums\n    - [ ] appropriate godot types like vector3\n    - [ ] fixed arrays","x":2720,"y":2000,"width":580,"height":240},
		{"id":"fa975478eba76e83","x":-700,"y":2980,"width":379,"height":1095,"type":"text","text":"```cpp\n\tenum Type {\n\t\tNIL,\n\n\t\t// atomic types\n\t\tBOOL,\n\t\tINT,\n\t\tFLOAT,\n\t\tSTRING,\n\n\t\t// math types\n\t\tVECTOR2,\n\t\tVECTOR2I,\n\t\tRECT2,\n\t\tRECT2I,\n\t\tVECTOR3,\n\t\tVECTOR3I,\n\t\tTRANSFORM2D,\n\t\tVECTOR4,\n\t\tVECTOR4I,\n\t\tPLANE,\n\t\tQUATERNION,\n\t\tAABB,\n\t\tBASIS,\n\t\tTRANSFORM3D,\n\t\tPROJECTION,\n\n\t\t// misc types\n\t\tCOLOR,\n\t\tSTRING_NAME,\n\t\tNODE_PATH,\n\t\tRID,\n\t\tOBJECT,\n\t\tCALLABLE,\n\t\tSIGNAL,\n\t\tDICTIONARY,\n\t\tARRAY,\n\n\t\t// typed arrays\n\t\tPACKED_BYTE_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_INT32_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_INT64_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_FLOAT32_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_FLOAT64_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_STRING_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_VECTOR2_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_VECTOR3_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_COLOR_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_VECTOR4_ARRAY,\n\n\t\tVARIANT_MAX\n\t};\n```"}
